            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pepper is softening, dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[125ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>peanut butter, red chilli relish </strong>and the juice<strong> </strong>of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1684831520635-x200.jpg",
