            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> chopped ginger</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>and <strong>carrot ribbons </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
