    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> plant-based Indonesian-style satay noodles</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>chopped peanuts </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
